data.description:
LOOK NO FURTHER - Gorgeous 3 bedroom, 2.1 bathroom, loft upstairs, 2 car garage home in Alta Vista. This home has everything you are looking for! Solar panels, water softener system, new roof 2023, recently installed water heater, gutters in front, sprinkler front, blackouts throughout. The great layout of this home allows to entertain family and friends at breeze. Kitchen features granite counter tops and eat-in kitchen.  Loft and ALL bedrooms are spacious with nicely sized closets. Owner's suite is on lower level, separate shower, garden tub, and large walk-in closet. Back yard is fenced and offers a shed and no back neighbors. Your options are unlimited with this home - come check it out!







Upgrades include - new roof April 2023, water heater replaced November 2022, gutters 2019, sprinkler system (front only)
